### Image API Usage Examples

### 1. List all images
GET http://localhost:8000/api/image
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 1.1. List images by user ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/image?userId=1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Get a specific image by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/image/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. Add a new image via file upload (RECOMMENDED)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/image/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

My First Image
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="userId"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
